{"id":161,"name":"虚空之眼","alias":"Velkoz","title":"维克兹","shortBio":"人们不太确定维克兹是否是符文之地上出现的第一个虚空生物，但可以确定的是没有第二个虚空生物能超过他的残忍和精明。他的同类通常都会吞噬或者破坏周围的一切，然而维克兹却一直在仔细观察并研究这个物质世界，以及世界上这些奇怪的好战生物，寻找虚空可以利用的弱点。但维克兹绝不是个被动的观察者，他会用致命的电浆射线回击任何威胁，甚至还能扰动世界本身的基础构造。","tacticalInfo":{"style":10,"difficulty":2,"damageType":"kMagic"},"playstyleInfo":{"damage":3,"durability":1,"crowdControl":2,"mobility":1,"utility":1},"squarePortraitPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-icons/161.png","stingerSfxPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-sfx-audios/161.ogg","chooseVoPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-choose-vo/161.ogg","banVoPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-ban-vo/161.ogg","roles":["mage"],"recommendedItemDefaults":["/DATA/Characters/Velkoz/Recommended/Beginner.json","/DATA/Characters/Velkoz/Recommended/VelkozARAM.json","/DATA/Characters/Velkoz/Recommended/VelkozFIRSTBLOOD.json","/DATA/Characters/Velkoz/Recommended/VelkozKINGPORO.json","/DATA/Characters/Velkoz/Recommended/VelKozNB.json","/DATA/Characters/Velkoz/Recommended/VelkozSR.json"],"skins":[{"id":161000,"isBase":true,"name":"虚空之眼","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-splashes/161/161000.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-splashes/uncentered/161/161000.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-tiles/161/161000.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Velkoz/Skins/Base/VelkozLoadScreen.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kNoRarity","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rarityGemPath":null,"skinLines":null,"description":null},{"id":161001,"isBase":false,"name":"战地机甲 维克兹","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-splashes/161/161001.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-splashes/uncentered/161/161001.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-tiles/161/161001.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters